<h2 class="sectionedit1"><a name="strncat" id="strncat">strncat</a></h2>
<div class="level2">

<p>

文法:

</p>
<pre class="cpp code cpp">    <span class="co2">#include &lt;cstring&gt;</span>
    <span class="kw4">char</span> <span class="sy2">*</span><span class="kw3">strncat</span><span class="br0">&#40;</span> <span class="kw4">char</span> <span class="sy2">*</span>文字列<span class="nu0">1</span>, <span class="kw4">const</span> <span class="kw4">char</span> <span class="sy2">*</span>文字列<span class="nu0">2</span>, <span class="kw4">size_t</span> カウント <span class="br0">&#41;</span><span class="sy4">;</span></pre>
<p>
strncat()関数は、最大で<code>カウント</code>文字数分の<code>文字列2</code>を<code>文字列1</code>に繋げて、NULL終端文字を追加し、結果の文字列を返します。
</p>

<p>
関連トピック: <a href="strcat" class="wikilink1" title="jp:string:c:strcat">strcat</a>, <a href="strchr" class="wikilink1" title="jp:string:c:strchr">strchr</a>, <a href="strncmp" class="wikilink1" title="jp:string:c:strncmp">strncmp</a>, <a href="strncpy" class="wikilink1" title="jp:string:c:strncpy">strncpy</a>
</p>

<p>
非標準の関連関数には<a href="http://www.cppreference.com/wiki/jp/string/c/strlcpy" class="wikilink2" title="jp:string:c:strlcpy" rel="nofollow">strlcpy</a>、<a href="http://www.cppreference.com/wiki/jp/string/c/strlcat" class="wikilink2" title="jp:string:c:strlcat" rel="nofollow">strlcat</a>があります。
</p>

